CatDescriptText: Men in photograph have two cornered hats on, some with tassels.  There are different inscriptions on the hats and patches such as, "Hospital Committee", "207", "Keystone", "PENNA".  The most visible men in image have bug patches on their vests and shirts.
TitMainTitle: Men and woman at party, some men wearing vests, two cornered hats, and pins with bug patches, possibly for VFW Military Order of Cootie
